<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>星期六早上，天一亮，乔伊就起来了，别人都还没起床。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她悄悄地穿上衣服，蹑手蹑脚地走下了楼梯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>昨天晚上，她写了一个任务清单。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天，她决心要完成上面的所有事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她走进了院子，靴子踩在结冰的草地上发出嘎吱的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47144</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一、二、三、四、五。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52066</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊数了数旁边的母鸡，还是少了一只。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可怜的母鸡。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55346</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她发现小水盆冻上了，于是去找砸冰的棍子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，乔伊在园子里发现了什么东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿！你在那儿干什么？” 是那只不见了的母鸡！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊跑过去把母鸡抱了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76411</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你还活着，太好了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76411</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她一边说，一边摸母鸡的头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你知道，逃出去是很危险的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊把母鸡放回了鸡圈，可她还是有一个疑问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你到底是怎么出去的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她仔细地查看了围栏的四周，但什么都没有发现。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，她听见凯蒂在叫她吃早饭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101223</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吃饭时，乔伊告诉妈妈和凯蒂她是怎么找到母鸡的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我得弄明白它是怎么跑出去的，不过我得先写关于领袖的发表。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈 ，我可以用你的电脑吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然可以。” 妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119900</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对了！妈妈，我还需要你所有的化妆棉和鞋油。” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈盯着凯蒂，“你到底要做什么？” 她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130300</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要做一个亚伯拉罕·林肯的胡子。” 凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“星期一发表时，我要戴着它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈笑了，“我等不及想看了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>早饭后，孩子们开始做作业。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂坐在厨房地板上做她的胡子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊坐在桌前，浏览网上关于领袖的内容。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麦古坐在乔伊脚边，闻凯蒂的鞋油味儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿，凯蒂，你知道关于哈丽特·塔布曼的事情吗？” 乔伊问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂放下化妆棉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不知道。我从来没听说过她。她是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“美国奴隶制存在时，她也曾是一个奴隶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她非常聪明，为了自由，她逃了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她还帮助过其他奴隶逃跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她冒着生命危险帮助他们向北一路逃到了宾夕法尼亚州和加拿大！” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195549</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她好勇敢啊！” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195549</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。” 乔伊说，“在内战期间，她甚至还为联邦军工作过。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202676</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂笑了。“嘿！我很想知道她是否见过亚伯拉罕·林肯！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把几个染了色的化妆棉贴到了下巴上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，哈丽特。” 凯蒂尽量模仿亚伯拉罕·林肯的声音说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你愿意为联邦军而战吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228013</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不是军人，林肯总统阁下，我是间谍！” 乔伊喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228013</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>双胞胎哈哈大笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，电话响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来接！” 凯蒂跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗨，奥利维亚。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有，我什么也没做。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊看了看被凯蒂弄得乱七八糟的地板。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有时候，她会为凯蒂和自己有太多的不同而感到惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，” 凯蒂大声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然了，我想练习滑冰旋转！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她挂断了电话，拍了拍乔伊的肩膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把你的书收起来，奥利维亚要过来，我们要去滑冰。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“麦古，别吃！” 凯蒂伸手从麦古嘴里掏出了化妆棉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊看了一眼外面，她想和奥利维亚、凯蒂练习滑冰旋转，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可任务清单上并没有这一项内容。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而且，她好不容易才想到了一个要发表的人物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊清了清嗓子，“我去不了，” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要写一篇关于哈丽特·塔布曼的发表！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>